emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Lila Williams, Dorothy Wilborn, Dorothy Conrad, and Betty Lewis, seated at North Park Lodge for Omega Psi Phi annual picnic
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 14, 1954, pg. 3 reads: "At Omegas' Picnic - Pittsburgh's chapters of Omega Psi Phi Fraternity held their annual picnic at North Park Lodge Tuesday afternoon and evening and, of course, there were plenty of ladies on hand to help the Omegas celebrate. Among them were those shown in the first photo on the left.  They are, left to right: Mrs. Lila Williams, Mrs. Dorothy Wilborn, Mrs. Dorothy Conrad and Mrs. Betty Lewis..."
